scene.message:
Nanjo: Yamaoka... don't die...{nl}
You won't leave me behind,{nl}
will you? ...Yamaoka.{waitkey}{ret}

Yamaoka: M-my goodness,{nl}
young master... please,{nl}
not that face...{waitkey}{clearbox}Such a fine face{nl}
you have... don't{nl}
let it go to waste.{waitkey}{clearbox}You are a fine young{nl}
Japanese man... A man must{nl}
stand on his own someday...{waitkey}{clearbox}This Yamaoka's service{nl}
ends here, I'm afraid...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: No, no, no!{nl}
I won't allow you to leave me.{nl}
Snap out of it, Yamaoka!{waitkey}{ret}

Yamaoka: This is{nl}
goodbye...{wait_fr:88}Young master...{nl}
one last thing...{nl}
a promise, between us...{waitkey}{clearbox}Please become the greatest{nl}
Japanese man this country{nl}
has ever seen!{wait_fr:100}{nl}
Koff... koff koff koff!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...Yes.{wait_fr:60} Yes.{nl}
Of course I will.{nl}
I'll show you that day.{waitkey}{nl}
So until then...{waitkey}{ret}

Yamaoka: That's my{nl}
young master...{nl}
{wait_fr:88}This Yamaoka will always...{nl}
live on in your heart...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Yamaoka? {wait_fr:60}...Hey!{nl}
Please... answer me...{nl}
Yamaokaaaaaa!!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey, {ctl0f:1}...{nl}
Did you hear those voices{nl}
just now?{waitkey}{nl}
He said he was me or{nl}
something like that.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I heard it too...{nl}
You think that was our{nl}
Persona just now?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: He said he'd lend us{nl}
his strength, so at least{nl}
he's not an enemy.{waitkey}{clearbox}If we're lucky, he might{nl}
do what we say...{waitkey}{clearbox}For now, let's just call{nl}
it a "Persona."{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yeah...{nl}
That's how it felt, but...{nl}
Something feels off.{nl}
Let's get outside.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I hope the school's{nl}
okay...{nl}
{ctl0f:1} Let's hurry outside!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: ...Nanjo,{nl}
in front of that old man,{nl}
you were just like a{nl}
kid, weren't you...{waitkey}{clearbox}The pain of losing someone{nl}
precious... there's nothing{nl}
harder than that.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Yamaoka...{nl}
What am I supposed to do?...{waitkey}{clearbox}Without you I'm alone...{nl}
No one will keep me in line...{waitkey}{clearbox}No one...{wait_fr:88}will be by my side...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Him crying like that...{nl}
That old man must've really{nl}
meant the world to him.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I feel bad for Nanjo,{nl}
but we gotta worry about{nl}
the living too.{waitkey}Come on, let's go save{nl}
Sonoda's mom!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: My...{nl}
so that's what happened...{nl}
Losing someone so precious...{nl}
can it change you so much?{waitkey}{ret}
